{Speech 2}{}{I'm sick and tired of this.@@We used to make jeans for sale and Encalve uniform. Now we are producing jumpsuits for those like you.@@Have you seen those cheap clothes at the stores? We made them.@@It's hell here.@@Those people have captured us.@@They almost don't feed us.@@They say "Work till sun's up." And it's always up here!@@Who're you?@@Why're you here?@@You've got funny eyes form. They're round.@@Shiu shihuau!}
